WEBVTT

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:01.583
GODA

00:00:01.583 --> 00:00:04.339
POLINA ZYNGER, KAUNAS, LITVA

00:00:10.757 --> 00:00:12.625
itster dertseylt a bisele

00:00:12.798 --> 00:00:16.989
vegn di gele lates. ir hot gezogt az ir hot getrogn gele lates.

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:17.330
ya.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:19.630
dertseylt vos iz, ver ⟨iz dos⟩ gemakht di lates

00:00:19.630 --> 00:00:21.635
vi hobn zey oysgezen, di lates.

00:00:21.843 --> 00:00:24.903
ot ⟨ikh hob di⟩ gantse tsayt itster getrakhtn, ⟨haynt⟩ bay nakht

00:00:24.903 --> 00:00:26.968
fun vanet hobn mir gekrogn di gele shtof?

00:00:27.108 --> 00:00:28.970
nor ikh veys az di mame

00:00:28.998 --> 00:00:31.659
hot ge- oysgeshnitn gele lates

00:00:31.901 --> 00:00:34.477
un mir hobn zikh ale ongeneyt gele lates.

00:00:34.533 --> 00:00:39.050
un vu, fun vanen, ikh hob UNK geven zeyer interesant, fun vanet hot di muter genumen gele shtof, az

00:00:39.731 --> 00:00:42.375
vayle geyn in gesheft koyfn iz nit gevezn.

00:00:43.072 --> 00:00:44.910
⟨fun⟩ vu hot men genumen veys ikh nit.

00:00:44.777 --> 00:00:47.471
un vifl lates hot yeder mentsh gemuzt trogn?

00:00:47.915 --> 00:00:50.592
tsvey lates, fun fornt un fun hintn.

00:00:51.088 --> 00:00:54.930
un a oyf yedn ayer beged, ir hot gehat mistome merer vi eyn kleydl.

00:00:55.087 --> 00:00:56.519
flegt men iberneyen.

00:00:56.519 --> 00:01:01.058
mir UNK oyf yede UNK lates; mir flegn iberneyen, nor dos ⟨merste flegn⟩ kleyder nit gehat.

00:01:01.058 --> 00:01:02.678
veynik ⟨ven⟩ geven kleyder shoyn.

00:01:02.698 --> 00:01:04.717
me flegt alts oysbaytn oyf broyt

00:01:05.212 --> 00:01:07.113
oyf zalts, oyf tsuker.

00:01:07.322 --> 00:01:09.173
azoy flegt men alts

00:01:09.853 --> 00:01:14.634
un ir vet ven nit iz flegt ir aroysgeyn in gas di ershe teg fun milkhome

00:01:14.634 --> 00:01:16.648
ven di daytshn zaynen shoyn geven in Kovne?

00:01:16.147 --> 00:01:16.786
neyn.

00:01:16.786 --> 00:01:19.533
di mame flegt mir nit lozn un ikh fleg nit aroysgeyn fun shtub.

00:01:20.298 --> 00:01:24.241
di mame flegt nor bay nakht in ovnt flegt zi aroysgeyn nokh, aynkoyfn vos nit iz.

00:01:24.433 --> 00:01:28.843
ober azoy nit dem, der foter flegt oykh nit geyn; di mame flegt nit lozn. di mame aleyn flegt rizikirn un geyn.

00:01:28.854 --> 00:01:30.522
un undz flegt zi nit lozn geyn.

00:01:30.522 --> 00:01:32.021
nit der bruder, nit ikh.

00:01:33.275 --> 00:01:35.110
mir flegn zitsn in shtub un vartn.

00:01:35.110 --> 00:01:38.670
un shpeter in kurtsn zaynen ⟨mir shoyn⟩ UNK geven a bafel alemen arayntsugeyn in geto.

00:01:39.030 --> 00:01:40.678
azoy vi mayn tante

00:01:40.734 --> 00:01:42.250
hot gelebt in

00:01:42.253 --> 00:01:43.144
rayon

00:01:43.144 --> 00:01:45.675
in tere- vu der geto hot gedarft zayn

00:01:45.695 --> 00:01:46.815
un dos iz gevezn

00:01:46.815 --> 00:01:47.512
in

00:01:47.923 --> 00:01:50.094
in forshtot fun Kovne.

00:01:50.100 --> 00:01:51.698
vi hot geheysn der forshtot?

00:01:51.399 --> 00:01:53.430
 Slabodke oyf yidish.

00:01:53.430 --> 00:01:55.106
un oyf litvish VILIAMPOLE.

00:01:56.512 --> 00:01:58.475
un di tante hot dortn gelebt

00:01:58.475 --> 00:01:59.564
in dem rayon.

00:01:59.564 --> 00:02:01.108
zi iz geven a lererin

00:02:01.153 --> 00:02:02.599
in a yidishe shul

00:02:03.195 --> 00:02:04.624
in Slabodke

00:02:04.832 --> 00:02:07.054
un zey hobn gehat a dire fun dray tsimern

00:02:07.346 --> 00:02:09.609
hot zi undz glaykh gezogt az "kumt

00:02:09.609 --> 00:02:12.599
zol eyde- kumt tsu undz un ikh vel aykh gebn a tsimer."

00:02:12.662 --> 00:02:16.808
hobn mir eyne fun di ershte zaynen mir arayn in geto, vayle mir hobn gevelt lebn bay ir.

00:02:17.049 --> 00:02:18.228
un dos iz gevezn

00:02:18.228 --> 00:02:20.824
di kleyn geto; dos iz geven oyf PANERIU gas.

00:02:22.618 --> 00:02:24.421
s'iz geven glat farn gas.

00:02:24.457 --> 00:02:25.838
tsu undz gegebn a tsimer

00:02:25.838 --> 00:02:28.840
un mir ale fir hobn gelebt dortn in tsimer tsuzamen mit di tante.

00:02:28.625 --> 00:02:30.560
ir hot gezogt "di kleyne geto."

00:02:30.417 --> 00:02:30.867
ya.

00:02:30.684 --> 00:02:34.357
vos iz di kleyne geto, un vos far an ⟨ort⟩ geto iz geven in Kovne?

00:02:34.329 --> 00:02:38.711
s'iz gevezn tsvey, ts- fun onfang iz geven alts eyns in zel- in Slabodke.

00:02:38.885 --> 00:02:41.523
⟨azoy vi⟩ es iz geven zyere a sakh mentshn; vayzt oys az

00:02:41.523 --> 00:02:44.924
un ikh shtel zikh for az in geto zaynen arayn fun onfang draysik toyznt

00:02:44.927 --> 00:02:47.531
drays- un ah umgefer draysik toyznt

00:02:47.531 --> 00:02:48.296
yidn.

00:02:48.656 --> 00:02:51.674
un azoy vi in di, arum, m'hot arumgetsoymt di geto

00:02:51.674 --> 00:02:54.458
iz geven veynik ort, hot men nokh genumen a teyl

00:02:54.458 --> 00:02:58.069
fun tsveyte gas, PANERIU; dos iz take UNK dertseyln; me darf do hobn

00:02:58.069 --> 00:02:59.248
vu tsu vayzn

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:02.010
hot men gemakht di kleyn geto.

00:03:02.010 --> 00:03:04.783
un grade mayn tante hobn dortn gelebt far der milkhome.

00:03:05.531 --> 00:03:08.276
a fayne shtub iz gevezn dortn, a hiltserne tsvey etazhne.

00:03:08.737 --> 00:03:10.040
hobn mir ⟨hobn⟩ dortn gelebt.

00:03:09.750 --> 00:03:10.622
dos

00:03:10.040 --> 00:03:12.312
un fun der UNK, eyn moment, dos iz geven fartsoymt

00:03:12.348 --> 00:03:16.108
un aribertsugeyn fun kleyn geto, az me flegt undz firn oyf arbet oyf groys geto

00:03:16.108 --> 00:03:17.287
fleg zayn a brik.

00:03:17.647 --> 00:03:19.964
flegt men, gemakht a brik, a durkh⟨UNK⟩ brik

00:03:19.964 --> 00:03:21.272
iber di gasn.

00:03:21.272 --> 00:03:22.316
oyf in der heykh.

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:26.012
un mir flegn aribergeyn fun kleyn geto oyf di groys geto.

00:03:26.675 --> 00:03:28.424
shpeter iz gevorn a bafel

00:03:29.730 --> 00:03:32.960
az a aktsye gevezn. mir ale zoln a-

00:03:33.392 --> 00:03:36.081
antshuldikt, bite, zogt, di hoyz

00:03:36.081 --> 00:03:38.972
iz geven a private hoyz fun ayer tante? zi iz geven

00:03:38.336 --> 00:03:39.343
a private hoyz.

00:03:39.315 --> 00:03:41.773
di tante iz geven a baleboste fun ⟨dem⟩ hoyz?

00:03:41.087 --> 00:03:41.826
neyn.

00:03:41.826 --> 00:03:44.017
a private. di tante hot dortn gedungen a dire.

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:46.836
a dray-tsimerdike dire.

00:03:46.065 --> 00:03:48.686
a dray-tsimerdike dire, un zey hobn gehat tsvey kinder.

00:03:48.686 --> 00:03:50.044
tsvey kleyne kinder.

00:03:50.064 --> 00:03:51.628
a yingele mit a meydele.

00:03:51.701 --> 00:03:54.759
un der f- der, ir man iz gevezn a bukhhalter in, in

00:03:54.759 --> 00:03:57.123
in a fabrik UNK, in a groyse fabrik

00:03:56.088 --> 00:03:59.812
un di tante, dos iz geven di mame's shvester oder dem foter's a shvester?

00:03:58.974 --> 00:04:01.393
dem foter's shvester. zi iz geven Lyuba, Lyuba.

00:04:01.393 --> 00:04:02.313
Lyuba Vald

00:04:02.313 --> 00:04:03.559
nokhn man's familye.

00:04:03.969 --> 00:04:07.186
un vos hot zi unterrikhtet, vosere zakhn?

00:04:06.281 --> 00:04:07.895
yidish, yidish.

00:04:07.665 --> 00:04:08.776
aha. a-

00:04:08.441 --> 00:04:09.077
yidish, vayl

00:04:08.776 --> 00:04:10.038
yidishe shprakh, ya?

00:04:09.386 --> 00:04:13.171
yidishe shprakh. zi iz geven a, in a yidishe folkshul, folkshul iz zi geven a lererin

00:04:13.171 --> 00:04:14.440
in Slabodke.

00:04:14.313 --> 00:04:16.332
un ir LIMUD iz geven di yidishe shprakh.

00:04:15.798 --> 00:04:17.370
ya, yidishe shprakh.

00:04:17.115 --> 00:04:17.852
i-

00:04:18.245 --> 00:04:21.423
i- ir hot, ir hot gehat gute batsiungen mit di, mit di tantn?

00:04:21.423 --> 00:04:23.606
ir flegt oft kumen tsu aykh far der milkhome?

00:04:23.848 --> 00:04:24.540
oft

00:04:24.540 --> 00:04:26.393
ikh fleg oft nit kumen, vayl es iz

00:04:26.393 --> 00:04:29.370
mir geven veynik tsayt; kh'fleg lernen; kh'fleg shpeter hobn fil z-

00:04:29.370 --> 00:04:30.662
eygene vos tsum ton.

00:04:30.699 --> 00:04:33.731
ober der ah foter mit di muter flegn dortn kumen.

00:04:33.855 --> 00:04:40.026
m'iz geven oykh sh- farnumen shabes, ven nit iz, ⟨shoyn⟩ flegt tsuzamenklaybn dos merste; in mitn vokh flegt men zeyer zeltn ver tsu vemen nit iz geyn.

00:04:40.098 --> 00:04:42.593
dos merste UNK ⟨flegt men⟩ tsuzamenklaybn shabes.

00:04:42.613 --> 00:04:43.893
a shabesdikn tog

00:04:43.893 --> 00:04:46.331
flegt UNK zey kumen tsu undz; ⟨zi⟩ flegt kumen di muter's

00:04:46.331 --> 00:04:50.000
di muter's shvester flegt kumen bay undz oyf tsholnt.

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.107
fargesn tsu zogn

00:04:51.107 --> 00:04:53.272
az shabes flegt men dokh nit kokhn

00:04:53.463 --> 00:04:55.590
flegn mir makhn tsholnt.

00:04:55.590 --> 00:04:56.776
un me flegt nemen

00:04:56.776 --> 00:04:58.919
a UNK fraytik flegt men

00:04:58.919 --> 00:04:59.924
in a top

00:04:59.924 --> 00:05:04.007
araynleygn dortn groypn, fleysh, zeyer fete fleysh, rinder fleysh.

00:05:04.007 --> 00:05:06.919
un me flegt avektrogn dos in a

00:05:06.947 --> 00:05:09.155
bekeray fun, fun broyt.

00:05:09.174 --> 00:05:12.578
un beshas me flegt aroysnemen di broyt flegt men araynshteln di tep in

00:05:12.633 --> 00:05:13.674
oyvns.

00:05:13.950 --> 00:05:16.023
un oyf shabes flegt men

00:05:16.023 --> 00:05:19.513
flegt, flegt mame mir shikn, fleg kumen, fleg shabes fleg ikh lernen

00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:21.068
fleg kumen fun klas

00:05:21.068 --> 00:05:24.470
fleg zi mir heysn geyn ikh zol oyfnemen aroysnemen brengen dem tsholnt.

00:05:24.682 --> 00:05:27.008
un ikh fleg UNK fun, fun bekeray

00:05:27.008 --> 00:05:29.092
un der bekeray iz gevezn oykhet onfang

00:05:29.092 --> 00:05:31.072
UNK ken es gedenken nokh vi haynt.

00:05:31.601 --> 00:05:34.420
iz fleg ikh brengen dem top mitn tsholnt.

00:05:34.487 --> 00:05:36.338
tsu fus flegt ir dos trogn?

00:05:36.697 --> 00:05:38.880
tsu fus ⟨vel⟩ ikh trogn, bashtimt tsu fus!

00:05:38.925 --> 00:05:43.796
s'iz geven ⟨mir vayl mir⟩ hobn gelebt oyf SAVANORIU dos UNK in mitn nit vayt dortn, un nit, nit, nit nit UNK

00:05:44.223 --> 00:05:46.940
azoy arum az ikh fleg tsu fus brengen dem tsholnt.

00:05:47.092 --> 00:05:49.990
un shabes flegt men nit kokhn; flegt men esn tsholnt.

00:05:50.450 --> 00:05:52.267
un s'iz gevezn UNK.

00:05:52.813 --> 00:05:54.979
un az ir zayt arayn in geto

00:05:55.007 --> 00:05:58.748
vi, vi iz gegangen ayer lebn di ershte vokhn in geto?

00:05:58.871 --> 00:06:01.650
v- vi hot ir zikh geshpayzt shoyn in geto?

00:06:02.027 --> 00:06:03.456
in geto

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:06.476
hobn mir nor gehat zakhn, me flegt baytn.

00:06:07.089 --> 00:06:09.176
beshas me flegt undz aroysfirn oyf arbet

00:06:09.772 --> 00:06:11.837
tomer flegt kumen litviner, flegn mir baytn.

00:06:11.837 --> 00:06:12.680
flegn zey undz gebn

00:06:12.680 --> 00:06:15.051
broyt, zalts, puter, shpek

00:06:15.071 --> 00:06:16.477
far, far, far di zakhn.

00:06:16.477 --> 00:06:19.034
shpeter iz gevezn in geto flegt men oykh gebn aza min

00:06:19.034 --> 00:06:20.755
RATION, ikh veys nit vi me zogt dos.

00:06:20.755 --> 00:06:24.290
vifl ⟨dortn⟩, vifl, vifl es bakumt undz. ikh gedenk nit vifl; ikh veys nor

00:06:24.290 --> 00:06:26.923
az eyn tsayt flegt men gebn farfrorene bulves

00:06:26.923 --> 00:06:31.387
flegt nor fun di bulves, fun di sho- UNK fun di sholekhts makhn latkes.

00:06:31.389 --> 00:06:34.910
gedenk ikh dos flegt men esn fun sholekhts fun farfrorene bulves.

00:06:36.266 --> 00:06:37.765
dos iz shoyn geven shpeter.

00:06:37.765 --> 00:06:41.824
nor fun onfang beshas ⟨m'iz arayn⟩ in geto hot men nokh gehat eygene zakhn; s'iz nokh geven vos tsu baytn; s'iz nokh geven

00:06:41.824 --> 00:06:44.411
fun onfang in geto iz nokh gevezn nit shlekht.

00:06:45.007 --> 00:06:48.067
me flegt, ⟨dos⟩ flegt zayn dortn kontsertn, yidishe kontsertn.

00:06:48.067 --> 00:06:50.570
flegt di, di yinglekh flegn shpiln futbol.

00:06:50.897 --> 00:06:52.883
un s'iz geven a plats vu tsu shpiln?

00:06:52.145 --> 00:06:53.962
s'is gevezn ⟨dort⟩ a lonke

00:06:54.896 --> 00:06:56.763
un oyf shpiln flegt men dortn shpiln.

00:06:57.562 --> 00:07:02.130
un shpeter, UNK nokh dem hot zikh ongehoybn di aktsyes, un me hot gevust mit vos es endikt zikh

00:07:02.557 --> 00:07:03.986
iz shoyn gevezn dan UNK erger.

00:07:03.553 --> 00:07:05.660
ir hot dertseylt, gezogt az,

00:07:05.660 --> 00:07:07.271
⟨vi ir⟩ flegt geyn oyf arbet.

00:07:07.299 --> 00:07:10.030
dertseylt a bisl, tsi ir ho- zayt aleyn gegangen?

00:07:07.310 --> 00:07:08.170
ya, me flegt

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.410
oyf tsv-

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:11.110
neyn, neyn

00:07:10.030 --> 00:07:15.039
tsu ayer muter, bruder, fl- ver fun ayer mishpokhe flegt geyn oyf arbet, un vos iz geven in der arbet?

00:07:14.775 --> 00:07:16.457
dos iz geven ZWANGSARBEIT.

00:07:16.698 --> 00:07:19.105
me flegt undz firn oyfn erodrom.

00:07:20.293 --> 00:07:24.287
me flegt, sh- roymen s- vinter flegt men roymen shney

00:07:24.613 --> 00:07:25.957
UNK mit lopates.

00:07:26.132 --> 00:07:28.372
zumer flegt men grobn griber

00:07:28.372 --> 00:07:31.592
trogn heltser, fun eyn s- fun eyn ort oyfn tsveytn ort

00:07:31.592 --> 00:07:34.170
azelkhene shvarts- shvartse arbet, ale shvartse arbet.

00:07:33.793 --> 00:07:36.032
ir zayt aleyn ⟨nokh⟩ gegangen oyfn erodrom?

00:07:35.177 --> 00:07:39.081
ikh hob UNK oyfn erodrom, oyfn erodrom hob ikh nit lang gearbet.

00:07:39.081 --> 00:07:42.658
shpeter hot men mir genumen arbetn do in firte shul, iz gevezn

00:07:42.669 --> 00:07:44.520
a kranke ⟨tsuzamenshtele⟩

00:07:44.778 --> 00:07:48.750
do in firte shul. me flegt brengen di daytshe soldatn UNK

00:07:48.761 --> 00:07:51.593
un shpeter flegt men dortn sortirn un firn zey vayter in Daytshland

00:07:51.593 --> 00:07:52.501
oyf heylung.

00:07:52.608 --> 00:07:56.833
un ikh hob dortn, i-, a grupe fun fir, finf meydlekh flegt men firn do.

00:07:56.833 --> 00:07:59.303
mir flegn vashn di fentster un vashn di diln.

00:08:00.624 --> 00:08:05.819
in eyn, in ey- eyn mo- mol, ⟨flegn⟩ dortn koridorn geven zeyer lange

00:08:05.819 --> 00:08:06.997
azoy vi in a shul

00:08:07.239 --> 00:08:10.350
gevashn di diln dortn, iz tsugegangen eyner a daytsh

00:08:10.361 --> 00:08:12.390
a hoykher, un er hot gezogt:

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:16.583
UNK gezogt, UNK arumgekukt, arumgekukt, beshas keyner zet nit un er hot aleyn gezogt:

00:08:17.702 --> 00:08:21.310
"Po-" ⟨er hot mir⟩ gezogt "Poline, PAULA," hot er gezogt vayl er hot UNK flegt kumen UNK

00:08:21.313 --> 00:08:24.665
"ICH WARTE ALLEIN WENN DER HITLER KAPUTT ⟨GEHT⟩."

00:08:25.194 --> 00:08:28.500
ober er hot zikh zeyer arumgekukt az keyner zol nit zen az mir UNK gezogt.

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:32.984
un shpeter hot er gezogt "bay- bayn ende in ende koridor oyfn fentster leyg ikh avek broyt mit margarin.

00:08:33.041 --> 00:08:34.757
beshas ale veln avekgeyn

00:08:34.830 --> 00:08:36.768
un kukn zikh arum keyner zol nit zen

00:08:36.768 --> 00:08:38.101
zolstu dos nemen."

00:08:38.101 --> 00:08:42.680
un beshas me vet dir fregn, tomer vet men fun vanet ⟨hostu dos⟩, zolstu UNK nit zogn az ikh hob dos avekgeleygt."

00:08:43.757 --> 00:08:45.760
azoy arum az s'iz gevezn azelkhene faln oykhet.

00:08:45.309 --> 00:08:47.295
der daytsh iz geven a fardvundeter?

00:08:47.942 --> 00:08:52.493
neyn, der daytsh iz gevezn nit keyn farvunderter; der daytsh iz dortn geven a ofitsir vayzt oys.

00:08:53.223 --> 00:08:55.310
nor mit a UNK iz er gevezn.

00:08:55.721 --> 00:08:58.112
er iz, er hot gehat a bis- ⟨EPOLOTNE⟩.

00:08:56.615 --> 00:09:03.600
ya, gehat, ya gehat. a OBERSTURMFUHRER tsi, ikh, ikh veys, ikh ken nit zogn. dos vel ikh nit zogn vayl ikh hob nit farshtanen dan in di ranges velkhe zaynen gevezn.

00:09:04.648 --> 00:09:08.051
nu, gefirt ⟨hobn zey⟩ undz oyf der arbet ale tog in der fri ts-.

00:09:08.917 --> 00:09:11.336
⟨tog flegn mir⟩. nor eyn zakh in geto iz geven gut.

00:09:11.336 --> 00:09:14.526
mir flegn kumen tsurik in shtub. mir flegn dort gefinen dem foter

00:09:14.526 --> 00:09:15.628
mit di muter.

00:09:15.937 --> 00:09:17.940
nor di aktsyes zaynen geven shreklekh.

00:09:18.333 --> 00:09:20.642
di ershte aktsye iz gevezn fun kleyn geto.

00:09:20.642 --> 00:09:21.804
in groys geto.

00:09:22.620 --> 00:09:25.284
m'hot undz ale; UNK fargesn dokh tsu zogn

00:09:25.284 --> 00:09:28.388
az mir hobn gelebt in Slabodke. tsuzamen hot gelebt dortn der zeyde.

00:09:28.408 --> 00:09:29.595
der zeyde fun Krozh.

00:09:29.595 --> 00:09:31.400
vayl etlekhe yor far dem

00:09:31.400 --> 00:09:34.275
in akht un draysikstn yor iz er gekumen tsu di tokhter shoyn

00:09:34.584 --> 00:09:38.105
un er hot gelebt bay di tokhter. er aleyn gevezn a provizor; er hot gehat zeyer a sakh bikher.

00:09:38.105 --> 00:09:40.015
zeyer a gelernter iz er gevezn.

00:09:40.828 --> 00:09:43.510
un er hot gelebt bay di tokhter.

00:09:43.510 --> 00:09:45.162
beshas iz gevezn kley- di

00:09:45.162 --> 00:09:47.589
 di kleyne aktsye fun di kleyn geto

00:09:48.810 --> 00:09:52.891
hot men gekumen, un alemen hot men aroysgetribn fun di shtiber mir zoln geyn ⟨oyfn⟩ plats.

00:09:52.893 --> 00:09:54.609
der zeyde mayner hot gezogt:

00:09:54.902 --> 00:09:55.549
"ikh

00:09:55.549 --> 00:09:57.073
heyb zikh nit fun bet.

00:09:57.551 --> 00:10:00.650
ikh blayb do. shtarbn vil ikh oyf mayn eygene bet."

00:10:01.415 --> 00:10:08.986
der foter, ikh gedenk, ⟨vi der fraynt⟩, vi der foter hot zikh bay im gebetn "foter, kum, me vet dir UNK do dershisn. foter, kum, efsher UNK mir veln durkhgeyn di aktsye."

00:10:09.347 --> 00:10:15.040
"neyn," zogt er. "ikh vel nit geyn." zikh ayngeshpart un nit gegangen. ikh bin arayngelofn. "zeyde," zog ikh, "kum mit undz tsuzamen ⟨mit⟩."

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:16.410
"neyn, ikh vel nit geyn."

00:10:16.518 --> 00:10:17.845
nit geyn, nit geyn.

00:10:17.902 --> 00:10:19.604
un undz iz gekumen di daytshn

00:10:19.604 --> 00:10:22.520
litviner un aroysgetribn fun shtib- fun shtub. un er iz geblibn.

00:10:22.897 --> 00:10:26.227
mir zaynen aroys oyfn plats. far undz iz gegangen di gantse p-

00:10:26.227 --> 00:10:27.887
⟨for⟩ dem di gantse mishpokhe

00:10:28.027 --> 00:10:32.125
geven undzere fraynt, oykhet fun Slabodke dortn, fraynt, dem foter's

00:10:32.125 --> 00:10:36.656
shvester's man dortn, nit di shvester's, an andere dortn UNK di gantse mishpokhe.

00:10:36.656 --> 00:10:40.172
oykhet mit kinder, zaynen gegangen far undz, un mir hinter zey.

00:10:40.768 --> 00:10:42.450
vi s'iz forgekumen di aktsye

00:10:43.333 --> 00:10:46.837
mir gibn a, far dem mir gibn a kuk. tsvey yunge bokherim

00:10:46.910 --> 00:10:49.098
firn dem zeydn untern orem.

00:10:49.475 --> 00:10:53.030
vayzt oys hobn di daytshn, un mir hobn gefregt dem zeydn vi azoy.

00:10:53.103 --> 00:10:55.100
zogt er, "a daytsh iz arayngegangen

00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:59.589
un genumen di tsvey bokherim ayngeshikt, "nemt im, un firt im aroys oyfn plats."

00:10:59.589 --> 00:11:00.995
vayl ⟨azoy⟩ muz zayn ⟨a⟩ ordenung.

00:11:01.406 --> 00:11:02.677
un shtelt zikh for

00:11:02.677 --> 00:11:03.932
az der zeyde

00:11:04.038 --> 00:11:07.453
iz durkhgegangen di aktsye. azoy ⟨alte⟩ mener flegn zey

00:11:07.453 --> 00:11:08.069
shikn

00:11:08.069 --> 00:11:09.247
oyf links.

00:11:10.940 --> 00:11:12.380
un, un im

00:11:12.380 --> 00:11:15.710
hot men geshikt vider oyf rekhts, heyst dos oyf der, in groyse geto.

00:11:16.323 --> 00:11:19.603
far undz, far undz ver zaynen geshtanen? zaynen ale

00:11:19.603 --> 00:11:21.347
g- de- di gantse mishpokhe.

00:11:21.723 --> 00:11:25.619
oykhet dortn gevezn ⟨Tatarski⟩ un Fishers a mishpokhe gevezn dortn, mit kinder.

00:11:25.619 --> 00:11:26.780
zey hot men geshikt

00:11:26.780 --> 00:11:27.692
oyf links

00:11:28.305 --> 00:11:30.240
un undz hot men geshikt oyf rekhts.

00:11:30.448 --> 00:11:33.733
antshuldikt. dos dertseylt ir mir vegn di kleyne aktsye ⟨oder⟩ vegn di gr-

00:11:32.523 --> 00:11:34.891
vegn di kleyne, vegn di kleyne aktsyes.

00:11:34.891 --> 00:11:36.702
vegn di kleyne, kleyn aktsye.

00:11:37.147 --> 00:11:39.861
di vos m'hot geshikt oyf rekhts ⟨heyst dos dortn⟩

00:11:39.881 --> 00:11:44.111
hobn UNK undz geheysn geyn durkhn brik, un undz alemen aribergetribn in groyse geto.

00:11:44.673 --> 00:11:47.865
di vos zaynen geblibn dortn hot men durkh nakhts

00:11:47.865 --> 00:11:49.795
zey gelozn vider in kleyn geto

00:11:49.795 --> 00:11:51.800
un oyf morgn, ikh hob shoyn dos nit gezen

00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:55.460
un oyf morgn alemen shoyn gezogt UNK bay di ⟨parkan⟩; UNK geven fraynt

00:11:55.460 --> 00:11:58.020
hot men gezen, m'hot zey avekgefirt ale oyfn nayntn fort.

00:11:58.410 --> 00:12:01.864
azoy arum az zey, azoy arum az m'hot likvidirt di kleyn geto

00:12:02.156 --> 00:12:03.433
in aza min oyfn.

00:12:04.485 --> 00:12:07.283
vos flegt ayer foter ton in di kleyn geto?

00:12:07.283 --> 00:12:10.081
er flegt oykh geyn arbetn oyf aerodrom tsi vu nit iz?

00:12:09.294 --> 00:12:11.853
ya, er flegt oykh geyn arbetn oyf erodrom.

00:12:12.905 --> 00:12:15.545
in kleyn geto iz nokh dakht zikh neyn iz nit geven keyn erodrom.

00:12:15.545 --> 00:12:21.055
s'iz geven andere arbet. azoy flegt men nemen ⟨d- oyf⟩ arbet. in shtot flegt men firn roymen di gasn, tsi vos. ot azelkhene arbet gevezn.

00:12:21.579 --> 00:12:23.433
in eyn rikhtik nokh

00:12:23.433 --> 00:12:25.168
s'iz nokh gevezn a bafel.

00:12:25.494 --> 00:12:29.010
dakht zikh s'iz geven ⟨oykhet⟩ fun kleyn geto, gehat. rikhtik, fun kleyn geto geven a bafel

00:12:29.010 --> 00:12:31.310
az di finf hundert yidn

00:12:31.502 --> 00:12:32.610
mener

00:12:32.750 --> 00:12:34.061
gelernte

00:12:34.185 --> 00:12:35.310
zoln zikh

00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:37.017
bavayzn

00:12:37.017 --> 00:12:38.189
oyf dem plats

00:12:38.189 --> 00:12:42.746
di vos kenen shraybn, vos kenen leyenen. me darf hobn gelernte finf hundert mentshn

00:12:42.746 --> 00:12:44.591
dortn oyf velkhe nit iz arbet.

00:12:44.732 --> 00:12:47.629
tsi sortirn bikher tsi vos, ikh gedenk nit vos zey hobn dortn gezogt

00:12:48.393 --> 00:12:52.674
nu, un d- mayn onkl iz dortn avek mit di ershte. de- de- der, der onkl.

00:12:53.135 --> 00:12:54.564
 der Vald?

