un dem pape mayner hot ⟨oykh⟩ gevelt geyn, vayl er hot gehalt- geendikt a rusisher gimnazye, nit kukndik dem vos er iz gevezn

00:13:03.570 --> 00:13:09.161
a zeyger makher, hot nor gehat geendikt rusishe, zibn klasn tsi vifl, un er hot gut gekent. er iz gevezn a gelernter azoy-o.

00:13:09.572 --> 00:13:13.813
iz, hot er gevelt oykh geyn, hot di mame gezogt "YAKOV

00:13:13.858 --> 00:13:16.603
ikh loz dir nit; du vest in ergets nit geyn."

00:13:17.385 --> 00:13:22.107
zogt er "vos, ale geyn; ot iz avek der mh, der Fisher iz avek."

00:13:22.107 --> 00:13:24.028
"neyn" ⟨zogt zi⟩. "du vest nit geyn."

00:13:24.185 --> 00:13:25.777
un azoy iz er geblibn.

00:13:25.910 --> 00:13:27.195
un di ale finf hundert

00:13:27.195 --> 00:13:28.696
vos zaynen avek, shpeter

00:13:28.696 --> 00:13:30.260
in ovnt hot men shoyn geredt

00:13:30.260 --> 00:13:31.152
mentshn hobn geredt

00:13:31.152 --> 00:13:33.852
az me hot gezen oyf a s-

00:13:33.852 --> 00:13:36.212
GRUZOVIK; vi zogt men GRUZOVIK oyf yidish?

00:13:35.458 --> 00:13:36.735
a last-AVTO.

00:13:36.285 --> 00:13:37.556
a last-AVTO.

00:13:37.567 --> 00:13:39.755
hot men shoyn gezen zeyere ale zakhn.

00:13:40.537 --> 00:13:42.151
UNK zey alemen hot men geshosn.

00:13:43.068 --> 00:13:44.981
un az mir zaynen azoy ariber in z- in geto.

00:13:44.981 --> 00:13:47.040
un in kleyn, in groys geto

00:13:47.085 --> 00:13:49.208
hot men shoyn der zeyde gevezn

00:13:49.228 --> 00:13:50.145
oykhet

00:13:50.145 --> 00:13:51.568
nor er iz gevezn

00:13:51.843 --> 00:13:53.795
mit di tante, mit Vald

00:13:53.936 --> 00:13:57.069
in eyn tsimer, un mir zaynen shoyn geven bazunder, undzer familye.

00:13:57.311 --> 00:13:58.574
un oyf morgn

00:13:58.574 --> 00:14:03.628
hot di tante gezogt az der zeyde hot genumen a ⟨tabletke s-⟩, vayl er iz geven a feldsher, ⟨er hot⟩ farshtanen

00:14:03.628 --> 00:14:04.218
un az

00:14:04.218 --> 00:14:05.560
zikh aleyn gemakht dem toyt.

00:14:05.560 --> 00:14:07.987
er hot gezogt az er vil shtarbn nor in eygene bet

00:14:08.685 --> 00:14:10.740
un azoy iz der zeyde mayner umgekumen.

00:14:10.710 --> 00:14:12.074
dertseylt a bisele

00:14:12.110 --> 00:14:15.533
 vi ⟨hot dos⟩ zikh bakumen az ayer foter hot gehat

00:14:15.536 --> 00:14:19.288
mo- heyst dos, ayer foter hot ge gehat a nomen vos

00:14:19.288 --> 00:14:20.891
me flegt im rufn in shtub

00:14:20.902 --> 00:14:24.069
un a nomen vos iz ge- farshribn gevorn in doku- dokumentn.

00:14:23.788 --> 00:14:25.930
in shtub flegt men in rufn YAKOV.

00:14:26.522 --> 00:14:28.322
un in dokumentn hot er geheysn Kopl.

00:14:28.867 --> 00:14:33.330
 vayzt oys hot er gehat tsvey nemen, ikh veys nit; UNK ikh hob ⟨gants tsayt ibergemeynt⟩ oykhet az er heyst nor YAKOV.

00:14:33.330 --> 00:14:36.078
un beshas ⟨zikh⟩ aroysgevizn nokh, nokhn krig az ikh hob genumen dokumentn

00:14:36.078 --> 00:14:37.839
vayzt oys er hot geheysn Kopl oykhet.

00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:39.690
UNK er iz geven Kopl Tatarski.

00:14:39.532 --> 00:14:42.294
un di mame flegt im rufn YAKOV, nit Yankl?

00:14:42.030 --> 00:14:43.121
neyn, neyn, YAKOV.

00:14:43.211 --> 00:14:44.285
YAKOV.

00:14:44.763 --> 00:14:46.394
YAKOV hot er geheysn UNK.

00:14:47.447 --> 00:14:48.639
azoy hobn mir gelebt.

00:14:48.307 --> 00:14:51.862
un ayer bruder flegt oykh geyn oyf der, oyfn arbet oysern shtot?

00:14:51.092 --> 00:14:55.592
ya. ya. un, un shpeter fun groys geto hot shoyn mayn bruder gearbet oyfn erodrom.

00:14:55.884 --> 00:14:58.040
oyfn ⟨drom⟩ iz zeyer shver arbet.

00:14:58.040 --> 00:14:59.570
fun fri biz bay nakht

00:14:59.570 --> 00:15:02.395
nit gegesn. UNK flegt men gebn a bisl zup dortn

00:15:02.398 --> 00:15:05.846
shpeter kumen, un ikh zog ⟨aykh⟩ dokh az in geto iz nokh gevezn zeyer gut.

00:15:05.846 --> 00:15:08.479
vayle me flegt kumen in shtub, flegt men gefinen di eygene.

00:15:08.479 --> 00:15:12.939
un di mame flegt nokh vos nit iz oyskokhn dortn. me flegt nokh vos oysbaytn; me flegt nokh hobn zakhn eygene.

00:15:13.181 --> 00:15:16.685
me flegt ⟨nokh⟩ brengen dortn dem, vifl dem RATION vos me flegt gebn

00:15:16.843 --> 00:15:20.578
tsi, oykh tsi shlekhte tsi gute. s'iz geven in geto verkshtatn

00:15:20.578 --> 00:15:24.785
dortn gelernt nokh; m'hot ge- a fakhman eyner oykh gelernt dortn

00:15:25.787 --> 00:15:28.397
un s'iz gevezn verkshtatn vos dortn flegt men arbetn

00:15:28.453 --> 00:15:30.420
far di ⟨daytshe⟩ flegt men ⟨arbetn⟩.

00:15:30.748 --> 00:15:34.624
un ayer muter, zi flegt blaybn in shtub, tsi zi flegt oykhet geyn?

00:15:34.494 --> 00:15:35.703
zi flegt blaybn in shtub.

00:15:35.895 --> 00:15:37.982
zi flegt nit geyn oyfn aerodrom?

00:15:37.329 --> 00:15:40.884
neyn; zi flegt ale mol oysmaydn, un zi, zi flegt blaybn in shtub.

00:15:41.227 --> 00:15:43.516
⟨mir⟩ hot alts gel- gelungen tsu blaybn in shtub.

00:15:44.180 --> 00:15:48.030
un der foter un ikh un der bruder flegn mir geyn ale oyf arbet.

00:15:47.876 --> 00:15:51.088
ir f- ir hot gezogt az in tsayt fun der arbet

00:15:51.099 --> 00:15:54.598
hot men gekoyft, gekent mit di litviner oysbaytn di zakhn

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:55.320
ya. y-

00:15:54.598 --> 00:15:55.999
oyf epes shpayz.

00:15:55.320 --> 00:15:56.920
ya, ya.

00:15:55.999 --> 00:15:58.434
ir hot aleyn aynteylgenumen in aza bayt?

00:15:58.676 --> 00:16:01.863
ikh aleyn hob nit ⟨aynteylgenumen⟩ in keyn bayt. ikh bin gevezn bazorgt

00:16:01.899 --> 00:16:04.875
fun, fun di mu- fun di muter un fun foter iz

00:16:04.875 --> 00:16:07.094
zey flegn mir nit lozn nit ⟨trogn⟩ vayle

00:16:07.097 --> 00:16:07.963
ikh vel aykh zogn

00:16:07.963 --> 00:16:12.190
vayle aroystrogn fun geto iz nokh gornisht. di ⟨zakhn⟩ iz flegt men nit kukn.

00:16:12.190 --> 00:16:14.535
ober arayntrogn in geto shpayz

00:16:14.555 --> 00:16:16.155
iz shoyn gevezn geferlekh.

00:16:16.175 --> 00:16:17.843
iz bayn geto toyer

00:16:17.843 --> 00:16:22.559
flegt men alemen durkhkukn un UNK zayn ale tar- torbelekh vos mer me trogt.

00:16:22.559 --> 00:16:23.918
un az me flegt gefinen

00:16:23.918 --> 00:16:26.059
flegt men oysshitn on me flegt nokh krign klep.

00:16:26.402 --> 00:16:27.977
me fleg shtark hargenen.

00:16:27.977 --> 00:16:30.080
azoy arum az mir flegt men

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:31.520
nit lozn baytn.

00:16:31.751 --> 00:16:34.884
der bruder flegt rizikirn zeyer; der bruder iz geven a rizikant.

00:16:31.785 --> 00:16:32.404
d-

