der foter nit aza min rizikant, ober der bruder geven a rizikant. er flegt f-

00:16:38.357 --> 00:16:41.789
flien, araynflien un UNK aroystrogn un baytn.

00:16:41.808 --> 00:16:45.390
UNK nokh gehat zeygerlekh, vayl der pape iz geven a zeyger makher. geven a sakh bay undz teyln

00:16:45.390 --> 00:16:47.256
flegt er fun di teyln tsuzamnshteln a zeygerl

00:16:47.256 --> 00:16:48.569
un flegt oysbaytn.

00:16:48.879 --> 00:16:51.213
UNK az in geto hot men nokh gekent; m'hot

00:16:51.213 --> 00:16:55.381
