00:16:55.381 --> 00:16:58.250
un me flegt shoyn visn ⟨UNK⟩erheyt UNK az se vet zayn a aktsye.

00:16:58.295 --> 00:17:01.597
shpeter iz geven di groyse aktsye.dos iz geven a shreklekhe aktsye.

00:17:02.227 --> 00:17:04.584
dem gantsn tog iz men geshtanen oyfn feld

00:17:04.707 --> 00:17:07.722
aroysgetribn in der fri alemen fun, fun di shtiber

00:17:08.893 --> 00:17:14.085
s'iz geven a re- aza min regn, aza min faykhter tog. dos iz gevezn dem tsva- akht un tsvantsikstn.

00:17:14.292 --> 00:17:17.184
ikh bin ⟨mispalel⟩ dos iz gevezn oktober, ya.

00:17:15.659 --> 00:17:16.801
oktober.

00:17:17.195 --> 00:17:20.412
dem akht un tsvantsikstn oktober, dos iz gevezn in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:17:21.937 --> 00:17:27.855
un glaykh in der fri, "alemen fun di shtiber, LOS, LOS." ale flegn muzn aroysgeyn fun di shtiber un shteyn oyfn plats, oyf

