s- geregnt, ge⟨UNK⟩

00:17:29.379 --> 00:17:30.622
tseshrokene

00:17:31.455 --> 00:17:32.929
un m'hot, m'hot gevust

00:17:32.929 --> 00:17:36.658
az oyber froyen aleyn veln geyn in, in rey, vet men zey glaykh firn oyf

00:17:36.658 --> 00:17:39.398
oyfn fo- oyfn fort, oyfn z- oyfn fort, oyf nayntn fort.

00:17:39.453 --> 00:17:42.536
oyber es vet nor geyn mer etlekhe mener, shtarkere

00:17:42.744 --> 00:17:47.964
vet, oyber UNK vet nor geyn a eltere froy un etlekhe sh- y- yunge, veln nokh durkhgeyn efsher.

00:17:47.964 --> 00:17:50.923
un oyb al- elt- not eltere aleyn, veln nit UNK.

00:17:52.228 --> 00:17:53.432
mit eyn vort

00:17:53.432 --> 00:17:57.048
mir zaynen gevezn UNK pape, di mame un ikh un der bruder.

00:17:57.712 --> 00:17:59.420
ober di tante mayne

00:17:59.420 --> 00:18:01.672
di tante mit di beyde tekhter

00:18:01.863 --> 00:18:03.190
dray tekhter

