un der bruder hot gezogt "gut; ikh vel geyn mit zey."

00:18:35.563 --> 00:18:37.211
vayzt oys iz geven bashert

00:18:38.651 --> 00:18:41.885
az zey zaynen durkhgegangen mitn bruder, un mir zaynen durkhgegangen.

00:18:42.313 --> 00:18:43.539
geven zeyer a sakh

00:18:43.612 --> 00:18:46.605
UNK froyen vos zaynen gegangen aleyn, un UNK merer froyen

00:18:46.605 --> 00:18:47.972
vos zaynen gevezn, an eltere

00:18:47.972 --> 00:18:50.010
zaynen ale avek oyfn nayntn fort.

00:18:50.430 --> 00:18:52.519
ir hot gevust far der selektsye

00:18:52.519 --> 00:18:55.925
az a teyl v- vet, vet zayn umge- umgebrakht?

00:18:55.745 --> 00:18:59.340
ya, men hot geredt az me vet firn oyfn nayntn fort.

00:18:59.340 --> 00:19:02.456
di UNK der day- der daytsh iz geshtanen oyf a benkl

00:19:03.255 --> 00:19:05.311
ya, oyf a benkl iz er geshtanen

00:19:05.311 --> 00:19:06.911
un er hot sortirt.

00:19:07.187 --> 00:19:09.327
in eyn zayt, oykhet rekhts

00:19:09.327 --> 00:19:11.535
iz geshtanen yidishe politsey.

00:19:12.047 --> 00:19:17.510
links iz geshtanen daytshishe un litvishe dakht zikh mir UNK gevezn. s'iz ⟨zeyer a⟩ tsayt gevezn, gedenk ikh UNK

00:19:17.531 --> 00:19:20.228
un ver es sh- oyf rekhts, bay di yidishe politsey

00:19:20.228 --> 00:19:21.291
gevezn rekhts

00:19:21.328 --> 00:19:23.449
un links in di, mit di politsey.

00:19:24.011 --> 00:19:26.064
un m'hot sh- m'hot, m'hot farshtanen.

00:19:26.542 --> 00:19:31.599
hobn andere ge⟨UNK⟩ durkhloyfn; m'hot zey geharget; m'hot nit gelozn. di geshreyen, di gevaldn iz gevezn groyse.

00:19:32.702 --> 00:19:33.830
dos iz geven

00:19:33.866 --> 00:19:35.261
a yomkiper iz gevezn.

00:19:35.267 --> 00:19:37.978
a, a lange tsayt hot gedoyert der sortirung?

00:19:37.848 --> 00:19:40.897
a lange tsayt. UNK ⟨geshtanen⟩, gefrorn

00:19:40.953 --> 00:19:42.297
vayzt oys bizn ovnt

00:19:43.738 --> 00:19:48.508
un shpeter ⟨hot⟩ undz alemen araynge⟨UNK⟩ heysn vider arayngeyn in di shtiber. dan iz shoyn di geto geven a halb puste.

00:19:49.458 --> 00:19:52.570
un dan hot men farklenert di geto. etlekhe gasn hot men opgeteylt

00:19:52.570 --> 00:19:55.880
di tsoym hot men gemakht kirtser, on m'hot shoyn gemakht klener di geto.

00:19:57.575 --> 00:19:58.886
un azoy hot men gelebt

00:19:59.330 --> 00:20:00.624
bizn aroysfirn

00:20:01.102 --> 00:20:02.058
in STUTTHOF.

00:20:02.857 --> 00:20:05.192
un, in di geto tsaytn

00:20:05.192 --> 00:20:09.132
say, say far di groyse aktsye, say nokh di groyse aktsye

00:20:09.132 --> 00:20:13.095
ayer lebn in geto hot zikh a bisl geendert tsi keyn zakh hot zikh nit geendert?

00:20:13.556 --> 00:20:16.436
alts, alts flegt dokh flegt zayn erger un erger.

00:20:16.728 --> 00:20:21.710
yedn tog flegt vern erger. fun onfang iz nokh ⟨geven beser⟩, m'hot zikh ⟨nokh⟩ hobn vos tsu baytn, me flegt hobn vos tsu ge-

00:20:21.710 --> 00:20:24.665
di shtimung iz nokh geven a besere. m'hot nokh azel- azoy nit forgeshtelt

00:20:24.665 --> 00:20:26.707
dem grestn umglik vos ken nokh zayn.

00:20:26.707 --> 00:20:28.681
m'hot nokh alts gelebt efsher, un efsher vet

00:20:28.681 --> 00:20:30.890
efsher darfn mir, efsher darfn zey hobn oyf arbet.

00:20:30.890 --> 00:20:32.822
efsher vet men undz oys⟨nutsn⟩ nor oyf di ARBEIT.

00:20:33.519 --> 00:20:35.520
efsher vet ⟨men es mer aktsyes nit⟩ zayn.

00:20:35.520 --> 00:20:38.812
oyb iz shoyn geven eyn aktsye, hot men geklert efsher vet shoyn mer keyn aktsyes nit zayn

00:20:39.054 --> 00:20:42.305
un azoy di gantse tsayt hot men gelebt nor mitn hofenung.

00:20:43.796 --> 00:20:45.883
un di gantse tsayt fun geto

00:20:45.939 --> 00:20:48.751
flegt ir geyn in dem militerishn shpitol arbetn?

00:20:49.128 --> 00:20:50.557
neyn, me flegt undz baytn.

00:20:51.086 --> 00:20:55.074
eyn mol in dem, f- in firte, vu di firte shkole, un eyn mol in a tsveytn shpitol.

00:20:55.074 --> 00:21:00.733
eyn mol hot men undz gefirt sh- in, in Shans, bay, bay sortirn z- militerishe zakhn.

00:21:01.633 --> 00:21:04.040
farshidene arbet. farshidene, farshidene arbet.

00:21:04.940 --> 00:21:07.078
un farshidn iz gevezn oykhet undz.

00:21:07.303 --> 00:21:09.612
beshas ikh hob gearbet in, in

00:21:09.612 --> 00:21:11.240
gevezn nokh a fayner fal

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:13.220
beshas ikh hob gearbet in

00:21:13.766 --> 00:21:14.908
in Shans

00:21:16.145 --> 00:21:17.509
bay,

00:21:17.509 --> 00:21:18.193
oykhet

00:21:18.193 --> 00:21:19.382
hot men mir genumen

00:21:19.382 --> 00:21:23.534
arbetn in a budke vu der daytsh z- flegt zikh dortn zitsn.

00:21:23.534 --> 00:21:25.086
un

00:21:25.086 --> 00:21:26.521
varemen zikh dortn

00:21:26.521 --> 00:21:30.284
fun firn dortn di rekhenung, un der ah, oyfn plats hobn gearbet yidn

00:21:30.284 --> 00:21:31.212
mener

00:21:31.232 --> 00:21:34.466
un froyen efsher oykh, UNK m'hot genumen in budke grade arbetn.

00:21:34.674 --> 00:21:39.157
trogn vaser, aynheytsn dem eyvele, aynheytsn, un trogn vaser tsu brengen dem UNK.

00:21:39.551 --> 00:21:42.482
un oyf, un litviner arbetn; zey hobn dortn geboyt.

00:21:43.770 --> 00:21:47.370
un se flegt kumen, yedn tog flegt kumen fun ARBEITS tsuzamenshtele

00:21:47.370 --> 00:21:52.750
flegt kumen eyne a litvinke un farshraybn ale arbeter di litviner ver es arbet vayzt oys tsum krign gelt.

00:21:52.750 --> 00:21:54.255
se flegt firn in statistike.

00:21:54.283 --> 00:21:58.597
un mir flegt zikh mit ir ale mol durkhreydn. zi flegt UNK gebn broyt.

00:22:00.054 --> 00:22:02.850
mit eyn, un i- s'iz gevezn vinter

00:22:03.108 --> 00:22:08.143
un ikh hob gehat dem mantl maynem oyfgehongen in budke oyf, oyf a tshvek, un ikh bin avek nokh vaser.

00:22:08.143 --> 00:22:11.372
avek nokh vaser bin ikh UNK a zeyger tsvelf beshas iz gevezn mitog tsayt.

00:22:11.732 --> 00:22:13.434
un ale, di arbeter

00:22:13.434 --> 00:22:17.400
zaynen gegangen oyf mitog, aroys oyf mitog, un zey flegn alts farbaygeyn far mayn budke.

00:22:17.739 --> 00:22:19.955
ikh kum mitn em- mitn emer fun vaser.

00:22:19.955 --> 00:22:21.061
ikh gib a kuk

00:22:21.061 --> 00:22:22.555
vayl mayn mantl iz nito.

00:22:22.555 --> 00:22:26.318
mayn mantl iz gevezn zeyer, nokh fun geto iz nokh gevezn UNK mantl nokh fun far di krig

00:22:26.318 --> 00:22:29.310
un er iz gevezn zeyer, me ken, flegt men im zeyer kenen erkenen.

00:22:29.636 --> 00:22:33.532
vayl er iz geven, a, a, ahm, ahm royter, shoyn aza min tunkl royter

00:22:33.532 --> 00:22:35.868
mit shvartse UNK ⟨kurtshinke⟩ arbl.

00:22:35.868 --> 00:22:37.376
nu, fun fel arbl.

00:22:38.664 --> 00:22:45.369
ikh ze dem mantl iz nito; ⟨vi⟩ darf men geyn tsurik in geto. mit eyn vort, dortn gevezn yinglekh vos flegn arbetn oyfn f- feld; efsher UNK gebn zeyer a rekl

00:22:45.369 --> 00:22:46.539
un gekumen tsurik.

00:22:47.203 --> 00:22:52.110
oyf morgn kumt di litvinerke undz UNK un zi shraybt vider di arbeter farshraybt

00:22:52.110 --> 00:22:54.574
zog ikh "du veyst" zog ikh, ⟨JANA⟩ hot zi geheysn, "du veyst" zog ikh

00:22:54.574 --> 00:22:59.156
"m'hot tsugeganvet mayn mantl." "oy," zogt zi, "dayn mantl hot men tsugeganvet?" zogt zi "ver hot dos gekent tsuganvenen?"

00:22:59.156 --> 00:23:01.085
UNK tsugeganvet. zogt zi "vart.

00:23:02.289 --> 00:23:04.545
vi ken dos zayn?" zog ikh "ya, UNK tsugeganvet."

00:23:05.006 --> 00:23:11.919
eyn mol fort zi mitn AVTO, mitn, mitn postn vos flegt kumen un flegt, flegt ir firn oyfn, oyfn arbet tsuzamenshtele

00:23:12.195 --> 00:23:15.227
un zi git a kuk oyf PUTVINSKIO, di gas.

00:23:15.536 --> 00:23:19.690
zi geyt eyne a lit- ⟨keyn⟩ yunge meydele geyt mit mayn ⟨mantl⟩.

00:23:19.690 --> 00:23:22.014
hot zi gezogt dem daytshn "HALT, HALT."

00:23:22.014 --> 00:23:23.127
shtel op dem mashin."

00:23:23.127 --> 00:23:27.101
un er zogt "vos klerstu zikh oyset?" UNK zogt zi "ikh bet aykh, shtel op di mashin."

00:23:27.112 --> 00:23:30.178
UNK hot er gefolgt, di litvinerke UNK bay zey gearbet

00:23:30.774 --> 00:23:33.637
UNK az di mashin. zi loyft tsu tsu ir un fregt ir:

00:23:33.828 --> 00:23:35.864
"fun vanet hostu dem mantl?"

00:23:35.972 --> 00:23:38.250
zogt zi "mayn onkl hot mir im gegebn."

00:23:38.250 --> 00:23:41.804
"ver iz dayn onkl? vi iz di familye ⟨dem onkl's⟩?" hot zi gezogt di familye dem onkl's.

00:23:42.705 --> 00:23:47.745
zi kumt tsu geyn oyf ibermorgn kumt zi tsu geyn mit mir "antshuldik, du veyst," zogt zi, ikh vel bald a kuk gebn in gantse reshime

00:23:48.138 --> 00:23:50.900
tsi der fam- di familye iz do tsi di familye iz nito."

00:23:51.108 --> 00:23:52.557
zi git a kuk ir reshime.

00:23:52.557 --> 00:23:53.870
punkt s'iz do oyf der reshime.

00:23:54.045 --> 00:23:55.946
zogt zi "der hot tsugenumen dayn mantl."

00:23:56.880 --> 00:24:00.202
zogt zi "UNK" zogt zi "⟨es vet⟩ kumen der daytsh."

00:24:00.202 --> 00:24:02.038
er flegt kumen mit a moto- oyf a mototsikl.

00:24:02.313 --> 00:24:06.909
flegt kumen alts UNK a kukn gebn eyner UNK a poshete, flegt er arumgeyn UNK ⟨vu⟩ hitn zey.

00:24:06.909 --> 00:24:08.614
un kukn vi me arbet, ober er flegt kumen

00:24:08.614 --> 00:24:09.440
a kuk gebn

00:24:09.440 --> 00:24:10.408
di arbet

00:24:10.616 --> 00:24:13.985
mit, oyf a mototsikl, mit a, mit a groye mashine UNK aza min-o.

00:24:14.666 --> 00:24:16.550
UNK tsi vos, a hoykher rang.

00:24:17.467 --> 00:24:18.761
zogt zi "du zog im."

00:24:18.851 --> 00:24:21.934
UNK zayn familye iz geven KOCH tsi vi dakht zikh, ikh gedenk nit.

00:24:22.023 --> 00:24:23.470
"nu, dertseyl im" zog ikh.

00:24:23.470 --> 00:24:26.940
"KOCH" zog ikh "UNK vet mir avekshisn ⟨oyb⟩ ikh vel dertseyln aza min mayse."

00:24:26.940 --> 00:24:29.375
zogt zi "neyn, dertseyl im un zog im."

00:24:30.039 --> 00:24:31.070
iz vos?

00:24:31.070 --> 00:24:32.458
kh'hob zikh genumen di ⟨dreystkeyt⟩

00:24:32.458 --> 00:24:33.830
kh'hob zeyer moyre gehat.

00:24:34.528 --> 00:24:36.829
kh'hob bahalt- ikh fleg kumen, fleg ikh zikh bahaltn

00:24:36.829 --> 00:24:39.585
vayl ikh hob gehat moyre zol mayn ⟨mir aroystraybn⟩ oyfn gas arbetn.

00:24:41.075 --> 00:24:44.090
er kumt tsu geyn, kler ikh vel ikh im zogn, ikh hob gezogt

00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:46.739
"Herr UNK" tsi vi ikh hob im gezogt

00:24:47.454 --> 00:24:49.608
"men hot mayn mantl GESTOHLEN."

00:24:50.323 --> 00:24:51.138
"ah!"

00:24:51.138 --> 00:24:53.591
hot er ongehoybn. "WER HAT DEIN MANTEL GESTOHLEN?

00:24:53.681 --> 00:24:55.700
DER SCHWEINE! DER HUNDE!

00:24:56.128 --> 00:24:57.607
hob ikh im gezogt di familye

00:24:57.815 --> 00:25:02.366
un gezogt vu er lebt, vayle di t- ⟨di litviner⟩ mir, ⟨JANA⟩ hot mir geheysn UNK ⟨un vu⟩.

00:25:02.709 --> 00:25:03.440
zogt er

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:05.271
"dayn mantl vet bay dir zayn tsurik."

00:25:05.308 --> 00:25:06.450
shtelt zikh for!

00:25:07.282 --> 00:25:09.959
un er hot zikh avekgef- -shtelt oyfn mototsikl

00:25:10.033 --> 00:25:11.850
avekgeforn dortn

00:25:12.193 --> 00:25:14.938
un UNK beshas er kumt ⟨hot er gezogt⟩ "der mantl vet bay dir zayn tsurik."

00:25:16.698 --> 00:25:18.228
un oyf morgn

00:25:18.352 --> 00:25:20.040
hot er UNK ⟨gebrakht⟩ dem mantl.

00:25:20.040 --> 00:25:22.310
der gim- der mentsh hot mir gebrakht dem mantl.

00:25:22.807 --> 00:25:23.302
ot

00:25:23.302 --> 00:25:26.784
UNK ⟨vos⟩ pasirt. bay zey ganvenen iz dokh erger far alts.

00:25:27.127 --> 00:25:30.750
ganvenen tor men nit. es darf zayn an ordenung. me darf aleyn avekgebn ale zakhn.

00:25:31.127 --> 00:25:34.651
 antshuldikt, ir hot gezogt az ir arbet in Shans.

00:25:34.651 --> 00:25:38.178
dos iz dokh gants vayt fun Kovner geto. vifl sho hot gedoyert tsu geyn

00:25:38.178 --> 00:25:40.031
in Shans un tsu kumen tsurik?

00:25:41.505 --> 00:25:45.932
a sho mistome, onderhalbn, un oyfn erodrom iz dokh oykh geven vayt fun geto, geyn oyfn erodrom

00:25:45.932 --> 00:25:48.292
un me flegt geyn nit oyf di laves, nor me flegt geyn oyfn

00:25:48.292 --> 00:25:50.242
vos iz geven mit shteyner; itstert iz asfaltirt.

00:25:50.242 --> 00:25:53.252
ober dan iz nokh keyn shtey- dan iz nit geven keyn asfalt; dan iz geven shteyner.

00:25:53.252 --> 00:25:58.790
flegt men ge- darfn geyn oyf di shteyner. s'iz geven zeyer shver tsu geyn. un shpeter hot men undz aribergehoybn fun geto in Shans oyfn lager.

00:25:58.835 --> 00:26:01.344
vayl mir hobn shoyn gearbet in Shans, hot men undz KAZARMirt

00:26:01.772 --> 00:26:03.630
un gearbet in ⟨Shanser⟩ Lager.

00:26:02.902 --> 00:26:05.684
un az ir flegt geyn arbetn fun Kovner geto

00:26:05.703 --> 00:26:08.131
say fun aerodrom, say dernokh in Shans

00:26:08.671 --> 00:26:11.536
zayt ir geven a groyse grupe mentshn, lemoshl in Shans?

00:26:12.437 --> 00:26:16.464
nu, a groyse, mistame fun fuftsik, fun zibetsik, fun hundert azoy-o.

00:26:16.368 --> 00:26:17.223
un

00:26:16.740 --> 00:26:18.422
a groyse, groyse kolone gevezn.

00:26:17.769 --> 00:26:20.193
un di kolone, ver hot dir gehit di kolone?

00:26:20.064 --> 00:26:21.712
daytshn, daytshe postns.

00:26:22.038 --> 00:26:23.889
a sakh postns zaynen geven bay ⟨der⟩

00:26:23.085 --> 00:26:24.727
dray. dray flegn firn.

00:26:24.727 --> 00:26:27.638
mentshn flegn rizikirn; me flegt aroysgeyn fun rey. me flegt zikh

00:26:27.638 --> 00:26:31.334
aroysgeyn b- baytn vos nit iz bay bakante, flegt men aroysgeyn un baytn.

00:26:31.334 --> 00:26:32.681
s'vet pasirn dos oykhet.

00:26:33.007 --> 00:26:35.229
ober ir perzenlekh flegt dos nisht ton.

00:26:34.745 --> 00:26:35.381
neyn.

00:26:36.247 --> 00:26:37.996
un ayer bruder, ayer fo-

00:26:37.513 --> 00:26:39.279
un mayn bruder flegt, flegt geyn.

00:26:39.487 --> 00:26:40.834
aroysgeyn rizikirn.

00:26:40.736 --> 00:26:41.523
er fle-

00:26:40.834 --> 00:26:42.977
un mir flegt, di mame flegt mir beshum oyfn nit lozn.

00:26:42.862 --> 00:26:45.539
vu hot der bru- vu hot gearbet ayer bruder?

00:26:45.275 --> 00:26:48.560
oyfn erodrom. dos ⟨merste⟩ hot er gearbet oyfn erodrom. er iz geven a erodromtshik.

00:26:49.055 --> 00:26:52.745
un dortn flegt er aroysgeyn fun, un hobn s- a kontakt mit litviner.

00:26:52.532 --> 00:26:56.745
er flegt hobn a kontakt; er flegt baytn dortn; er flegt brengen in shtub vos, vos UNK tsum esn.

00:26:56.835 --> 00:26:59.648
der pape andere mol flegt ⟨baytn⟩; der pape iz geven a kleyner rizikant.

00:27:00.463 --> 00:27:02.162
un der bruder dos ⟨merste bruder⟩.

00:27:02.741 --> 00:27:05.033
UNK me flegt baym toyer flegt men zeyer hitn

00:27:05.070 --> 00:27:05.891
vos er

00:27:06.825 --> 00:27:10.490
zeyer flegt men kukn, hargenen, un a- oysshitn dos vos me flegt brengen

00:27:10.689 --> 00:27:12.214
un s'iz gevezn ts-

00:27:12.214 --> 00:27:14.632
s'iz do azelkhene lider, ⟨iz nor⟩ do yidishe lider.

00:27:16.055 --> 00:27:17.045
yo.

00:27:16.393 --> 00:27:17.805
baym, baym geto toyer

00:27:18.840 --> 00:27:21.450
brent a fayer, un di shrek iz groys.

00:27:23.058 --> 00:27:26.326
dertseylt, bite. ir hot gezogt az in geto

00:27:26.619 --> 00:27:29.313
iz forgekumen a gevise ⟨KAZARMATSYA⟩.

00:27:29.606 --> 00:27:32.553
vos iz dos a ⟨KAZARMATSYA⟩ un ven zi iz forgekumen?

00:27:33.943 --> 00:27:40.378
ven iz zi forgekumen ikh, ot itster, ikh vil aleyn zikh dermonen; ikh ken zikh nit dermonen. vayzt oys tsi in dray un ferts- tsi in fir un fertsikstn yor shoyn far

00:27:40.378 --> 00:27:44.707
farn likvidiren di geto, sh- beshas di geto hot nit UNK, mistame in dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:27:44.707 --> 00:27:46.200
mir hobn gelebt in Shans

00:27:46.200 --> 00:27:48.044
dan in, oykhet barakes.

00:27:49.164 --> 00:27:51.436
vos, un me hot aykh aroysgehoybn fun geto.

00:27:51.138 --> 00:27:53.388
aroysgehoybn, aroysgefirt fun, fun geto

00:27:53.388 --> 00:27:56.367
un, un gelebt hobn mir shoyn dan in Shans, in barakes.

00:27:56.367 --> 00:27:57.498
geven nares

00:27:57.498 --> 00:27:58.980
untn un oybn.

00:27:59.323 --> 00:28:04.433
mir hobn gelebt oyfn, mir hobn ge- undzer ge- nare iz geven di untershte, un oybn hobn gele- geleygt shlofn andere.

00:28:04.433 --> 00:28:05.201
breter.

00:28:05.201 --> 00:28:06.152
oyf breter.

00:28:06.613 --> 00:28:07.907
nares iz gevezn.

00:28:08.570 --> 00:28:10.168
azoy vi in, in STUTTHOF.

00:28:10.545 --> 00:28:13.951
de- zogt mir bite: vifl mentshn zayt ir geven

00:28:13.953 --> 00:28:17.796
KAZARMirt fun Kovner geto in Shanser lager?

00:28:19.286 --> 00:28:20.833
ken bashtimt nit zogn.

00:28:21.480 --> 00:28:24.388
ken bashtimt nit zogn, nor mener, mit froyen, mit kinder

00:28:24.388 --> 00:28:26.520
aza gantse, groyse barak

00:28:27.133 --> 00:28:29.422
ikh vel zogn a lign efsher; ikh vel zogn a fir finf hundert.

00:28:30.407 --> 00:28:32.191
un efsher veyniker un efsher merer.
